                     <interp inst="t18200517-73-person788" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have a garden by Mr. Holdup's. Having been repeatedly robbed, I sat up to watch, and, about half past three o'clock in the morning, I saw the prisoner come from the prosecutor's garden. I followed and secured him at the end of Margaret-street, with the hatchet and hammer under his coat, and the hoe in his hat. He said he brought them from Wapping.</p>
